casebody.data:
MAHONING CTY. BAR ASSN.
v.
VERKHLIN. 2017-1756 Supreme Court of Ohio. April 19, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

DISCIPLINARY CASES

On certification of default. On relator's motion for remand. Motion granted. This matter is remanded to the board of professional conduct for default proceedings pursuant to Gov.Bar.R. V(14)(F). The interim default suspension imposed against respondent on January 11, 2018, shall remain in place while this matter is pending before the board. Proceedings before this court in this case stayed until further order of this court.
